            <p>ΛΙΘΟΝΔΙΟ<lb/>ΡΙΖΟΝΤΑ<lb/>ΚΩΜΔΗΡΑϹ<lb/>ΚΑΙΚΑΠΑΡ<lb/>
               <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>ΙΓΗ<gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
